data.description: This stunning custom built one owner home by the lake could be your dream home come true! Owner states that courthouse records for square footage is incorrect. Upstairs area was just finished this Spring, which now makes this a 2180 sq ft 4 bed 3 full bath home and has not been updated in the tax records yet.  Come see this lovely home sitting on a beautiful one-acre lot with mature trees and it's just 1/4 mile from Sunnyside Ramp on Lake Oologah. You can be on the lake fishing before the fish wake up! You're sure to love the large wrap around porch of this secluded home, sitting back off the road hidden amongst the huge Oak and Redbud trees. Stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, with a large pantry and lots of cabinet space. The upstairs central H/A is new, a fresh coat of paint inside and out, with a high impact resistant roof replaced in the last 5 years. The living area has 19' vaulted ceilings with 9' ceiling throughout the house giving it a very spacious feel. All bedrooms have walk in closets, the Master and second bedroom are downstairs. A whole house vacuum system really helps with household chores. An oversized garage has epoxy floors, a work area and a new insulated garage door. The Rainguard guttering around the house has a transferrable lifetime warranty. This home could be your private retreat by the lake. Take stroll to the beach and enjoy the lake view.  This is one you're surely going to want to come and see it today!
